{
  "page": "Tourney at Duskendale in honor of Lord Darklyn's wedding",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <b>tourney at Duskendale in honor of Lord Darklyn's wedding</b> was held in <a href=\"/index.php/Duskendale\" title=\"Duskendale\">Duskendale</a>, seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Darklyn\" title=\"House Darklyn\">House Darklyn</a>, in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_72_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">72&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_at_Duskendale_in_honor_of_Lord_Darklyn%27s_wedding&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> celebrated the marriage of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Darklyn\" title=\"House Darklyn\">Lord Darklyn</a> to a daughter of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Theomore_Manderly\" title=\"Theomore Manderly\">Theomore Manderly</a>. The tourney included a squire's melee in which Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Aemon Targaryen</a> was the victor, defeating his younger brother Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Baelon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Baelon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Baelon</a>. Aemon also distinguished himself in the lists, and he was subsequently <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knighted</a> for his jousting skills. After returning to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, the newly-made knight took to the skies as a <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonrider\" title=\"Dragonrider\">dragonrider</a> on <a href=\"/index.php/Caraxes\" title=\"Caraxes\">Caraxes</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Attendees\">Known Attendees</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_at_Duskendale_in_honor_of_Lord_Darklyn%27s_wedding&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Attendees\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/32px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/48px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/64px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Aemon Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/32px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/48px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/64px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Baelon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Baelon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Baelon Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/32px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/48px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/64px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Targaryen\" title=\"Alyssa Targaryen\">Alyssa Targaryen</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_at_Duskendale_in_honor_of_Lord_Darklyn%27s_wedding&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Long Reign - Jaehaerys and Alysanne: Policy, Progeny, and Pain.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404200605\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.035 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.072 seconds\nPreproc